title: Nunes, hero of Stanford’s win over Arizona in 2012, recalls 54-48 shootout
text:
Photo: Jason O. Watson, Getty Images Quarterback Josh Nunes #6 of the Stanford Cardinal passes against the Arizona Wildcats during the fourth quarter at Stanford Stadium on October 6, 2012 in Palo Alto, California. Quarterback Josh Nunes #6 of the Stanford Cardinal passes against...
The last time Stanford and Arizona met, each team amassed exactly 617 yards in one of the wildest offensive shows in recent Cardinal history.
